1
00:00:43,780 --> 00:00:46,780
=Strange Tales of Jiangcheng=
=Episode 14=

2
00:00:47,140 --> 00:00:49,500
(Jiangzhou Police Station)

3
00:00:53,800 --> 00:00:55,770
The murderer killed someone
right in front of the police.

4
00:00:56,040 --> 00:00:57,740
This is a blatant provocation.

5
00:01:00,550 --> 00:01:02,100
Compared to the first preview,

6
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,460
the time,

7
00:01:03,750 --> 00:01:04,590
the content,

8
00:01:04,590 --> 00:01:05,750
and the book has all changed,

9
00:01:06,000 --> 00:01:07,660
but only the writing style remains the same.

10
00:01:08,830 --> 00:01:10,580
Before the murderer engaged with us,

11
00:01:10,830 --> 00:01:12,540
he had already calculated every step

12
00:01:13,190 --> 00:01:14,300
very precisely.

13
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:15,840
Even the appearance of corpse miasma

14
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:16,740
at Panlong Hill

15
00:01:17,160 --> 00:01:18,460
was part of his plan.

16
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:19,970
All these indicate

17
00:01:20,190 --> 00:01:21,840
that the murderer's criminal behavior

18
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:23,100
is highly systematic.

19
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:24,960
He has keen insight,

20
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:26,050
and exceptional intelligence.

21
00:01:26,440 --> 00:01:29,300
The ways he punished the victims

22
00:01:30,040 --> 00:01:31,590
are evident that he is engaging

23
00:01:31,590 --> 00:01:32,430
in a game with the police.

24
00:01:32,800 --> 00:01:34,380
I agree with Mr. Qin's analysis.

25
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:36,380
I checked the almanac just now.

26
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:38,170
Yesterday was Grain Rain Day.

27
00:01:38,480 --> 00:01:39,830
With the arrival of this solar term,

28
00:01:39,830 --> 00:01:40,670
everything revives

29
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,540
and corpse miasma is bound to occur.

30
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,340
A man chooses to commit a crime

31
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:48,150
because his inner desires

32
00:01:48,150 --> 00:01:49,100
are not satisfied.

33
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:50,850
Some do it for money,

34
00:01:51,270 --> 00:01:52,500
some for revenge,

35
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:54,250
and some to vent their emotions.

36
00:01:55,030 --> 00:01:55,870
In short,

37
00:01:55,920 --> 00:01:56,910
once they embark

38
00:01:56,910 --> 00:01:57,750
on the path of crime,

39
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:59,270
their desires

40
00:01:59,270 --> 00:02:00,760
will become apparent.

41
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,940
But the murderer in this case

42
00:02:02,310 --> 00:02:03,280
has not yet shown

43
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,120
his desires.

44
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:06,170
This is the biggest challenge.

45
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:07,690
Without desires,

46
00:02:08,430 --> 00:02:10,340
there is no breakthrough point.

47
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,680
Does the murderer just want us

48
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:13,520
to be spectators?

49
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,240
Let's split into two teams.

50
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:20,640
On team

51
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:23,030
find outs the clues left by the murderer.

52
00:02:23,030 --> 00:02:24,870
The other team finds out

53
00:02:24,870 --> 00:02:26,100
why the victim was Han Da.

54
00:02:26,310 --> 00:02:27,400
Han Da and Che Jingwen

55
00:02:27,400 --> 00:02:28,280
must be related

56
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,150
somehow

57
00:02:29,150 --> 00:02:30,030
unlike they showed.

58
00:02:30,030 --> 00:02:31,800
We need to find the connection
between the two.

59
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,640
Captain Song,

60
00:02:32,710 --> 00:02:34,540
I request to handle this part myself.

61
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,780
Let Chen and the others do it.

62
00:02:37,270 --> 00:02:38,900
I am more familiar with Mr. Che.

63
00:02:39,110 --> 00:02:39,990
It would be better

64
00:02:39,990 --> 00:02:40,830
for me to investigate it.

65
00:02:41,110 --> 00:02:42,290
The murderer is so brutal.

66
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:43,680
If something happens to you,

67
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,970
how can I explain it to Commander Lei?

68
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,380
Yes. Dr. Fan,

69
00:02:46,640 --> 00:02:47,850
let us handle it.

70
00:02:48,550 --> 00:02:50,010
I think we can let Xiaofan try.

71
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:51,920
Xiaofan,

72
00:02:51,990 --> 00:02:53,710
aren't you good friends
with Lieutenant Zou?

73
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:54,550
Ask him for help.

74
00:02:54,990 --> 00:02:56,250
Lei's Army has many soldiers.

75
00:02:56,480 --> 00:02:57,690
They can turn Jiangzhou upside down.

76
00:02:58,080 --> 00:02:59,200
There must be some clues.

77
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,040
That's right.

78
00:03:03,080 --> 00:03:03,920
Mr. Qin,

79
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:05,730
thank you for helping me just now.

80
00:03:06,870 --> 00:03:07,710
It's nothing.

81
00:03:08,590 --> 00:03:09,830
But you have to promise me,

82
00:03:09,830 --> 00:03:11,030
you must take Zou Jing with you

83
00:03:11,030 --> 00:03:12,010
and protect your own safety.

84
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:13,270
Don't worry.

85
00:03:14,320 --> 00:03:16,360
Recently, I visited
all the major tea houses in Jiangzhou

86
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,410
and bought a lot of tea leaves.

87
00:03:18,030 --> 00:03:19,640
After comparison, it was confirmed

88
00:03:19,640 --> 00:03:21,310
that the tea you drank
at Che Jingwen's house

89
00:03:21,310 --> 00:03:22,400
came from Wuyuxuan.

90
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,710
That tea house

91
00:03:23,710 --> 00:03:24,690
was owned by the victim Han Da.

92
00:03:25,180 --> 00:03:26,100
(Wuyuxuan)

93
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:30,310
On the day you went outfor a walk,

94
00:03:30,310 --> 00:03:31,450
you went to find this?

95
00:03:34,000 --> 00:03:34,870
I see.

96
00:03:34,870 --> 00:03:36,200
I will proceed

97
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,040
with this clue.

98
00:03:37,550 --> 00:03:39,170
Okay, waiting for your good news.

99
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:17,970
Mr. Huo,

100
00:04:18,510 --> 00:04:19,950
you should be writing your novel
at home.

101
00:04:19,950 --> 00:04:20,960
Why are you following me?

102
00:04:20,960 --> 00:04:21,800
What are you up to?

103
00:04:22,560 --> 00:04:23,960
Miss Fan, you misunderstand me.

104
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,040
How dare I have any intentions

105
00:04:25,040 --> 00:04:26,140
to hurt you?

106
00:04:26,470 --> 00:04:27,310
To be honest,

107
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,370
I have been excited all morning.

108
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:30,960
The incident at Panlong Hill

109
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,760
suddenly inspired me.

110
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:34,880
I plan to use this case as a blueprint

111
00:04:34,880 --> 00:04:36,880
to create a new novel.

112
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:39,170
If nothing unexpected happens,

113
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,520
this work

114
00:04:40,520 --> 00:04:42,320
will become a significant piece

115
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,320
in my writing career.

116
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:44,540
Alright, do as you please.

117
00:04:44,760 --> 00:04:45,790
You can follow me.

118
00:04:45,790 --> 00:04:46,970
But let me tell you,

119
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:49,270
you cannot interfere
with my investigation.

120
00:04:49,270 --> 00:04:50,160
Rest assured, Miss Fan.

121
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,470
I promise to be so well-behaved

122
00:04:51,470 --> 00:04:52,710
that you will forget

123
00:04:52,710 --> 00:04:53,700
I'm even here.

124
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:58,820
(Wuyuxuan Teahouse)

125
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:07,370
That rat,

126
00:05:08,150 --> 00:05:09,680
I thought he was held up

127
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,260
by some girl from Huanyinglou.

128
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:12,710
I was even planning

129
00:05:12,710 --> 00:05:13,780
to confront him when he returned,

130
00:05:14,470 --> 00:05:15,410
but he...

131
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:18,290
he would never come back.

132
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:20,100
Don't you and Mr. Han

133
00:05:20,590 --> 00:05:21,490
have any children?

134
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:26,800
Then may I ask,

135
00:05:27,030 --> 00:05:28,100
did Mr. Han ever mention

136
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,320
Che Jingwen to you

137
00:05:29,320 --> 00:05:30,460
when he was alive?

138
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:31,960
Who?

139
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:33,020
Che Jingwen.

140
00:05:38,150 --> 00:05:39,850
Before Mr. Han disappeared,

141
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:41,930
did he have any unusual behavior,

142
00:05:42,350 --> 00:05:43,790
or did anyone

143
00:05:43,790 --> 00:05:44,730
frequently come to see him?

144
00:05:45,230 --> 00:05:46,070
Or,

145
00:05:46,200 --> 00:05:47,320
did he mention someone

146
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:48,260
to you multiple times?

147
00:05:49,350 --> 00:05:51,050
I really can't remember anything.

148
00:05:59,670 --> 00:06:00,510
Miss Fan,

149
00:06:00,510 --> 00:06:01,950
(Wuyuxuan Teahouse)
where are we going next?

150
00:06:03,710 --> 00:06:04,920
It's almost mealtime.

151
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,520
I want to treat you to a meal.

152
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:08,610
