156
00:06:14,440 --> 00:06:16,370
How about I treat you to a taste?

157
00:06:17,520 --> 00:06:18,610
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

158
00:06:19,260 --> 00:06:20,940
(Jushangfang)

159
00:06:21,780 --> 00:06:24,540
(Jushangfang Reopens)

160
00:06:28,590 --> 00:06:29,930
You must be Qingyao.

161
00:06:30,150 --> 00:06:31,230
My father told me

162
00:06:31,230 --> 00:06:32,520
that Miss Jiangyun's Jushangfang

163
00:06:32,520 --> 00:06:33,470
has reopened

164
00:06:33,470 --> 00:06:34,310
thanks to you.

165
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:36,540
Lawyer Qin helped me before.

166
00:06:36,760 --> 00:06:37,930
He asked me a favor.

167
00:06:38,320 --> 00:06:39,970
I couldn't turn him down.

168
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:42,810
Your cooking skills are
as good as Miss Jiangyun's.

169
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,470
Thank you for the compliment, Miss Fan.

170
00:06:44,470 --> 00:06:46,320
The meal is on the house.

171
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:48,150
Please enjoy it.

172
00:06:48,150 --> 00:06:49,370
That won't do.

173
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:50,760
Mr. Huo said

174
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:51,730
he's paying the bill today.

175
00:06:52,560 --> 00:06:54,520
Yes. I said I would pay the bill.

176
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:56,020
These dishes are nothing.

177
00:06:56,270 --> 00:06:57,700
Just give me a discount.

178
00:06:59,030 --> 00:07:01,340
Alright, then I won't disturb you two.

179
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:02,400
Enjoy your meal.

180
00:07:04,470 --> 00:07:05,460
Miss Fan, please sit.

181
00:07:09,960 --> 00:07:11,560
Miss Fan, you've worked hard on the case.

182
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,540
Eat more.

183
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,850
I'm willing to be at your service.

184
00:07:15,150 --> 00:07:16,270
If you need my help,

185
00:07:16,270 --> 00:07:17,340
just let me know.

186
00:07:20,830 --> 00:07:21,900
In the future,

187
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:24,120
if there's an opportunity,

188
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,590
please speak well of me

189
00:07:25,590 --> 00:07:26,910
in front of the Commander.

190
00:07:26,910 --> 00:07:29,030
Maybe write a preface for my new book.

191
00:07:29,030 --> 00:07:29,870
I would be

192
00:07:30,320 --> 00:07:31,260
so grateful.

193
00:07:32,200 --> 00:07:33,520
So grateful.

194
00:07:33,520 --> 00:07:34,360
Mr. Huo,

195
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:36,710
I have a question
that I've been curious about.

196
00:07:36,710 --> 00:07:37,640
I hope you can enlighten me.

197
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:38,520
Miss Fan,

198
00:07:38,520 --> 00:07:40,050
just call me Huo.

199
00:07:40,470 --> 00:07:41,790
Feel free to ask any questions.

200
00:07:41,790 --> 00:07:44,050
I will tell you everything I know.

201
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:45,840
Huo,

202
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:46,800
in your opinion,

203
00:07:47,150 --> 00:07:49,080
what else could

204
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,080
Mr. Che and Han Da

205
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:51,020
have in common?

206
00:07:51,960 --> 00:07:53,140
Well,

207
00:07:54,670 --> 00:07:56,370
Che Jingwen has no friends.

208
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:57,900
It seems like

209
00:07:58,400 --> 00:07:59,620
he doesn't need friends either.

210
00:08:00,310 --> 00:08:01,690
I don't know

211
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:04,210
why he chose to live like a monk.

212
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,050
My debut work,

213
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:08,780
The Death Lantern,

214
00:08:09,030 --> 00:08:10,430
wouldn't have been published

215
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:12,170
without his help.

216
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:13,570
But even so,

217
00:08:13,910 --> 00:08:15,210
I never felt that Jingwen

218
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:16,900
truly opened up to me.

219
00:08:17,640 --> 00:08:19,400
So the only time

220
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:21,450
he and Han Da could meet

221
00:08:22,030 --> 00:08:23,140
is probably

222
00:08:24,360 --> 00:08:26,090
when they went to Wuyuxuan to buy tea.

223
00:08:29,840 --> 00:08:30,680
It seems

224
00:08:31,550 --> 00:08:33,170
I don't really know Mr. Che at all.

225
00:08:34,910 --> 00:08:36,570
Given Mr. Che Jingwen's character,

226
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:38,050
what he considered precious

227
00:08:38,360 --> 00:08:40,690
is certainly not precious
in the worldly sense.

228
00:08:42,070 --> 00:08:43,150
That tea

229
00:08:43,150 --> 00:08:44,900
must have special meaning to him.

230
00:08:46,550 --> 00:08:47,740
You mean,

231
00:08:48,030 --> 00:08:48,870
there is such a person

232
00:08:48,870 --> 00:08:49,950
who is particularly important

233
00:08:49,950 --> 00:08:50,790
to Che Jingwen.

234
00:08:51,190 --> 00:08:53,270
He once bought tea at Wuyuxuan Teahouse,

235
00:08:53,270 --> 00:08:54,480
and then gave it to Che Jingwen.

236
00:08:54,480 --> 00:08:55,320
Is it right?

237
00:08:55,430 --> 00:08:56,740
We cannot rule out this possibility.

238
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,790
This person who is very important
to Che Jingwen

239
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:04,900
is the key to this case.

240
00:09:05,430 --> 00:09:06,270
That's right.

241
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,900
You go to Che Jingwen's house now.

242
00:09:08,310 --> 00:09:09,150
No matter what,

243
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:10,640
I think this person

244
00:09:10,640 --> 00:09:12,450
must have appeared in his life before.

245
00:09:12,450 --> 00:09:13,980
According to
Locard's Exchange Principle,

246
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,810
whether it's a person or an object,

247
00:09:16,190 --> 00:09:17,450
when the two meet,

248
00:09:17,670 --> 00:09:19,540
there are only two results:

249
00:09:20,270 --> 00:09:21,110
First,

250
00:09:21,360 --> 00:09:22,500
something is left behind.

251
00:09:22,790 --> 00:09:23,630
Second,

252
00:09:24,190 --> 00:09:25,410
something is taken away.

253
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:28,090
Alright, I'll go now.

254
00:09:33,150 --> 00:09:34,090
Aren't you coming with me?

255
00:09:37,150 --> 00:09:38,380
You go to Mr. Che's house.

256
00:09:38,760 --> 00:09:41,000
I'll stay here
and read Huo Qingxin's third novel

257
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:41,840
to look for clues.

258
00:09:42,400 --> 00:09:43,240
The two of us

259
00:09:43,430 --> 00:09:44,760
are the best partners.

260
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:45,600
Miss Fan,

261
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,140
I just thought of something.

262
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,140
- Quickly, tell me.
- At that time,

263
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:52,720
the novel The Death Lantern

264
00:09:52,720 --> 00:09:53,810
sold very well.

265
00:09:54,270 --> 00:09:57,980
So the publishing house asked me
to write a sequel,

266
00:09:58,310 --> 00:10:00,170
still with Cheng Sen as the protagonist.

267
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:01,760
But the first few paragraphs

268
00:10:01,760 --> 00:10:03,170
were challenging to me.

269
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:04,570
So I asked

270
00:10:05,030 --> 00:10:07,050
Jingwen for some advice.

271
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:09,910
Jingwen,

272
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:11,120
please help me.

273
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:12,520
Look, I've been troubled by it

274
00:10:12,520 --> 00:10:13,360
for several days now.

275
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,240
If you don't help me,

276
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:15,330
what am I going to do?

277
00:10:16,400 --> 00:10:17,790
I'm afraid I can't today.

278
00:10:17,790 --> 00:10:18,980
I have to go to Nu Mountain.

279
00:10:19,880 --> 00:10:22,020
Jingwen, please be kind.

280
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:23,610
I'm really sorry, Qingxin.

281
00:10:23,610 --> 00:10:25,110
I have an appointment
early in the morning

282
00:10:25,110 --> 00:10:26,280
with Monk Chenhai from Xiyin Temple.

283
00:10:26,280 --> 00:10:28,000
I absolutely cannot miss it.

284
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:29,580
When I have time,
I will definitely help you.

285
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:32,240
Jingwen.

286
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:33,980
This Monk Chenhai

287
00:10:34,360 --> 00:10:36,440
was probably

